cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about video object segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a new network architecture that learns a powerful representation of the target and background appearance in a single forward pass, which involves probabilistic generative models. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
